{
  "stem": "22972.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when he came to power-- when he engineered his election as chancellor and took over, became total dictator-- he had a spider's web in place all over the country.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had informants in place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He had that pyramid was built, and he had found most of these warped minds from the bottom 2% of the barrel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Which could happen in America.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All you would need is a Senator McCarthy to come along during-- not in the 19-- not in 1950, when we had a great period of prosperity.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But let him come along in 1930, when we had a Great Depression in America.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that is what Hitler found.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Fertile ground, and unemployment, and malcontents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And Miller Millville's father had been a Gauleiter, right from the beginning, a supervisor of the whole district of all the littler Nazis.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And Frau Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Neumann got several visits that we all knew about from the Gauleiter, Millville.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And nobody ever talked when Milla Millville was around, because I'm sure that she had several people arrested, Jews as well as pure Aryans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "If she didn't like them, she'd talk to her dad, and that was enough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But anyway, the class picnic was always looked forward to with great anticipation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "A day of total freedom in the country, im Gruenewald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we got to the school the morning of the picnic and the bus was there and all the children piled into the bus, and the eight of us stood there very uncertainly, not knowing what we should do.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we eventually, when all the other kids were sitting in the bus, we were eventually allowed to sit in the last rows, reminiscent of what was going on in America, in the South.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
